{"tid":1179574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喝泥水吃飛蛾 夏威夷婦森林迷路17日獲救","createTime":"2019-05-31T08:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T08:31:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f361e68d7cb2a4266dfe6548bb12a900670ab5c","tid":1179574,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190527/20688464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688464&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=e47c9399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688464&h=9123f51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190527/20688464</a><br />\n<br />\n喝泥水吃飛蛾<br />\n夏威夷婦森林迷路17日獲救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190527/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=b3794d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埃勒獲救後在醫院床上跟親友合照。路透社<br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷一名女子在叢林失蹤17天後上周五奇蹟尋回。35歲的埃勒（Amanda Eller）本月9日在毛伊島佔地逾809公頃的馬卡瓦森林保護區失蹤。當地出動數千名義工、警員、消防員搜索，終於在離行人徑入口約11公里處尋回。她被發現時受輕傷，但精神狀態良好，已送院治理，說曾吃飛蛾充飢。<br />\n<br />\n搜救人員估計艾勒從原處至少已步行約48公里。埃勒的好友約克指她被發現時正嘗試循水源到達海邊但被深谷所困，又指今次並非她首次看見直升機，前幾次她揮手均無人看見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高處跌下受傷<br />\n<br />\n約克指埃勒起初花了兩天嘗試回到停泊在入口的車輛但不果，之後她放棄並開始尋找水源。第三天她不慎滑倒並從20呎高處跌下，腿部受傷，膝關節半月板軟骨撕裂。第四天她的鞋被沖走，只能赤腳而行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190527/large/a1503b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2Fa1503b.gif&h=3df64a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搜救隊17日內以熱成像無人機和衞星定位等技術尋人。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190527/large/a1503c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2Fa1503c.gif&h=f15c4a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功尋回女兒，埃勒父親（右）擁抱搜救隊長。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n埃勒失蹤時只穿着薄背心、運動內衣和瑜伽褲，而森林晚上的氣溫可跌至15℃。約克說：「她說最慘是捱凍。她當時只能棲身野豬洞穴，以蕨類植物或隨手找到的任何東西包裹身體保溫。她最想雨停，好讓她不用再喝泥水和捱凍。」她又指艾勒以野果如草莓番石榴果腹，甚至吃過停在她身上的兩隻飛蛾。<br />\n<br />\n她的父親約翰．埃勒直言：「我們已開始失去希望。當我收到消息時完全難以置信。森林的地勢險要，置身其中十分容易失去方向和迷路。」埃勒一家為救她在網上籌得7.6萬美元（59.28萬港元），計劃用餘款改善行山徑安全。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nNSA涉知情不報兼卸責<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n曾阻約翰遜入閘 英環境大臣爭拜相"},{"pid":"e58992e3b67748565175651c5d27d3cd844f9220","tid":1179574,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"頂到咁多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e92c08ae76a9fe68c03301b06849aa3cd1c3f52","tid":1179574,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58992e3b67748565175651c5d27d3cd844f9220","tid":1179574,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"頂到咁多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"搵返個陣仲係精神狀態良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157f3c7b1fa0280be6ddedabdf6c5167afde810e","tid":1179574,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"應該已經俾外星人替換左或者寄生左啲嘢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c7538d0d0ec6249d2c8a3e6d42b3ee7faa811a","tid":1179574,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53728bb363b4cce39cd4788e